trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of elements that are used to configure routing.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.RoutingSection"></xref> class.
Gets the configuration element that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.BackupEndpointElement"></xref> objects.
A collection that defines the configuration section that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.BackupEndpointElement"></xref> objects.
Creates a filter table using the specified name.
A routing table with the specified name must exist in the configuration file for the current AppDomain; otherwise an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> occurs.
The name of the filter table to create.
A filter table with the specified name.
Gets the configuration element that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement"></xref> objects.
A collection that defines the configuration section that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterElement"></xref>.
Gets the configuration element that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterTableEntryElement"></xref> objects.
A collection that defines the configuration section that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.FilterTableEntryElement"></xref> objects.
Gets the configuration element that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.NamespaceElement"></xref> objects.
A collection that defines the configuration section that contains a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.Configuration.NamespaceElement"></xref> objects.
